# Comprehensive .dockerignore template for ASP.NET Core applications
**/docs/
**/logs/
*.md
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------
# .NET Build and Release Outputs
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------
# Exclude local compilation and publish artifacts to avoid environment conflicts
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/publish/

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------
# IDE and Editor Files
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------
# Visual Studio source control, user-specific, and temporary configuration files
.vs/
**/*.user
**/*.suo
**/*.sln.docstates
**/*.lscache

# Visual Studio Code workspace settings and caches
.vscode/

# Rider / IntelliJ JetBrains editor specific files
.idea/

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------
# Source Control and CI/CD
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------
# Exclude Git history and pipeline files unless specifically required inside the container
.git/
.gitignore
.github/
.gitlab-ci.yml
azure-pipelines.yml

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------
# Operating System Garbage Files
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------
# macOS specific folders
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride

# Windows specific thumbnail and desktop files
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------
# Frontend and Package Manager Dependencies (If using SPA/WebOptimizer)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------
# Exclude local node packages to let the Dockerfile build them natively if needed
**/node_modules/
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------
# Docker Configuration Files
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------
# Prevent Docker configurations from copying into themselves
Dockerfile
.dockerignore
docker-compose*